review_blob: I cant imagine a beer that is trying to be a cocktail more accurate than this. I think the bittering agent is key. The orange, cherry, bourbon barrel and Rye are all pretty spot on. Even the worry of too much slimy Rye is lifted. Crack this open with friends, wine drinkers who think all beer is the same, whisky lovers and the adventurous. Great job Kevin at Listermanns/Triple Digit
